data.description: Ready for new owners, this 3 bedroom 1 bath home over full basement is all spruced up. Freshly painted and new flooring throughout. Newer metal roof.  Gas forced air heat, central air and range can be electric or gas.   Sit on your wood deck on rear of home and enjoy your privacy fenced yard.  1 car detached garage and 8 x 10 storage shed.
